    "QuestInfo": [
      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u5C71\u6797\u306E\u8352\u6CD5\u5E2B",
        "Client": "\u52A0\u5DE5\u5C4B\u306E\u30CF\u30E2\u30F3",
        "Description": "\u5927\u793E\u8DE1\u3067\u3001\u30D3\u30B7\u30E5\u30C6\u30F3\u30B4\u304C\r\n\u901A\u884C\u4EBA\u306B\u8FF7\u60D1\u3092\u304B\u3051\u3066\u304A\u308B\u3002\r\n\u3061\u3087\u3046\u3069\u3001\u9020\u3063\u3066\u3044\u305F\u304B\u3089\u304F\u308A\u306B\r\n\u30E4\u30C4\u3081\u306E\u7D20\u6750\u304C\u5FC5\u8981\u3067\u3042\u3063\u305F\u3086\u3048\r\n\u307E\u3055\u3057\u304F\u4E00\u6319\u4E21\u5F97\u306E\u597D\u6A5F\u2026\u3002\r\n\u7D20\u6750\u306F\u30EF\u30B7\u304C\u78BA\u4FDD\u3059\u308B\u3002\r\n\u304A\u306C\u3057\u306B\u306F\u3001\u72E9\u731F\u3092\u4EFB\u305B\u305F\u3044\u3002",
        "Target": "\u30D3\u30B7\u30E5\u30C6\u30F3\u30B4\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Monkey Wrench in Your Plans",
        "Client": "Hamon the Blacksmith",
        "Description": "In order to separate Magnamalo\r\nfrom the Rampage, I need to\r\ncomplete my device. In order to\r\ndo that, I need materials from a\r\nBishaten. One has been spotted\r\nin the Shrine Ruins. Depart at once!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Lancer la machine",
        "Client": "Hamon le forgeron",
        "Description": "Pour s\u00E9parer le Magnamalo et\r\nla Calamit\u00E9, je dois terminer\r\nma machine, et pour \u00E7a, il me\r\nfaut des mat\u00E9riaux provenant\r\nd\u0027un Bishaten. \u00C7a tombe bien,\r\nun a \u00E9t\u00E9 aper\u00E7u au Temple\r\noubli\u00E9. Allez, au boulot !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Bastoni fra le ruote",
        "Client": "Hamon il fabbro",
        "Description": "Per separare il Magnamalo\r\ndalla furia, devo completare\r\nil mio dispositivo. Per farlo,\r\nmi servono materiali di\r\nBishaten. Ne hanno avvistato\r\nuno alle Rovine sacre.\r\nDevi partire subito!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Affenartiges Material",
        "Client": "Hamon der Schmied",
        "Description": "Um Magnamalo von der Randale\r\nzu trennen, muss ich mein\r\nGer\u00E4t fertigstellen. Daf\u00FCr\r\nbrauche ich Material von einem\r\nBishaten. In den Heiligen\r\nRuinen wurde einer gesichtet.\r\nGeh gleich los!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Bishaten.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Guardi\u00E1n de las monta\u00F1as",
        "Client": "Hamon el herrero",
        "Description": "Se ha visto un Bishaten en el\r\ndel Templo olvidado, y resulta\r\nque estoy haciendo una m\u00E1quina\r\nque requiere materiales de uno\r\nde ellos. Matar\u00EDamos dos\r\np\u00E1jaros de un tiro: yo consigo\r\nmateriales, y t\u00FA una caza.",
